  EffectDiscription_JPN: 
  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[Digivolve] Lv.5 w/[Fallen Angel]/[CS]\_trait: Cost 3 \n\nWhen
    this card would be played, if your opponent has 10 or more cards in either their
    hand or trash, reduce the play cost by 5.\n[On Play] [When Digivolving] Your
    opponent trashes cards in their hand so that they have 6 cards left. If this
    effect didn't trash, you may play 1 level 5 or lower [Fallen Angel]\_trait Digimon
    card from your trash without paying the cost.\n[End of Your Turn] [Once Per Turn]
    If your opponent has 6 or more cards in their hand, they trash 1 of them. Then,
    if they have 5 or fewer, delete 1 of their lowest level Digimon."
